+/*
+ * FX2 (Logic 8) analog data converter.
+ *
+ * The analog mux outputs frames of ana_channel_cnt * 3 * 2 bytes.
+ * Each channel produces 3-byte triplets, with byte 2 (bits 0-7 of
+ * the 24-bit value) containing the 8-bit ADC sample. Each channel
+ * appears twice per mux cycle (two time-interleaved samples).
+ *
+ * The raw 0-255 value maps linearly to a voltage range that is
+ * stored in per-device calibration data (ana_vmin/ana_vmax).
