+ * Frame layout for N analog channels:
+ *   triplet 0: CH0 sample A (3 bytes, ADC in byte 2)
+ *   triplet 1: CH0 sample B
+ *   triplet 2: CH1 sample A
+ *   triplet 3: CH1 sample B
+ *   ...
+ *   triplet 2N-2: CHn sample A
+ *   triplet 2N-1: CHn sample B
